# 🎓 College Management Web API

This project — **CollegeProject** — is a .NET 8 Web API built using the **Repository Pattern** and **Database-First Approach**, providing secure CRUD operations on **Students** and **Courses** with **JWT Authentication and Authorization**.  
It also includes a separate **College_View** API layer for frontend integration.


## 🚀 Features

✅ **Entity Framework Core (Database-First)** – Reverse-engineered from SQL Server using EF Core  
✅ **Repository Pattern** – Clean separation between Data Access and Business Logic  
✅ **JWT Authentication** – Secure login and token-based authorization  
✅ **CRUD Operations** – Full create, read, update, delete for Students and Courses  
✅ **Role-Based Authorization** – Only authenticated users can access specific endpoints  
✅ **Swagger Integration** – Interactive API testing interface  
✅ **CORS Enabled** – Allows web client apps to consume this API  
✅ **College_View API** – Lightweight view API for simplified frontend access  


